column5: hey yall, i heard from a buddy that burleigh falls in peterborough was on fire today, ppl were hauling in walleye from shore, is the season for that division even open? if so we are going this weekend if not we will go on the opener, anyone ever fished up there?
Don't know about there - but the Kawartha Lakes open 2nd saturday in May  Don
Looking at the regs, it looks like it's a sanctuary till after the friday after the second saturday in May  Edit So essentially you can fish it the 3rd saturday in May.
hmm ok thnx guys, he didnt call the mnr, not sure if he knew the regs or not, they just drove by and stopped, so second or 3rd saturday in May will do it, thnx
